ACSIOR Ltd means Analysis, Computer System Integration and Operation Management. The company is a leading system integrator. We are a Bulgarian private company, established in 1991. We have been a member of the Bulgarian Association of Informational Technologies (BAIT) since its establishment, and since 1995 the company has been a member of the American Chamber of Commerce in Bulgaria.
The company is a leading system integrator and offers:
• Analysis, development and application of customer-oriented software;
• Building up and system integration of complex information systems;
• Technical support and services for computer systems, software, communication systems and networking, specialized computer devices and periphery of leading IT providers;
• IBM authorized warranty and post warranty service;
• Consultancy, development and implementation of software applications for business management, database design;
• Implementation and maintenance of Electronic Data Interchange (EDI) systems between store chains and their suppliers as per EANCOM standards;
• Embedded Systems design and engineering (Hardware and Software);
